<p style="font-size:1.05em; line-height:1.7; color:#2d3748;">Welcome to your first lesson. Before we get into <em>how</em> to create content that sells, you need to understand what TikTok Shop actually is, how creators earn from it, and why right now is the best time to start. Watch the video above first, then walk through the slides below — each one has a short explanation to go with it, and a couple of quick checks along the way so you can make sure it's landing.</p>

