<p style="line-height:1.7; color:#2d3748;">Here's the stat that changes everything: <strong>80% of TikTok Shop revenue comes from creators with fewer than 50,000 followers.</strong> Not the mega-influencers. Not the people with blue ticks and PR lists. Normal creators, with normal followings, earning real money every single day. The marketplace is growing rapidly, and the opportunity is wide open — you just need to start.</p>

