<p style="line-height:1.7; color:#2d3748;">The gateway is deliberately low because TikTok wants creators on Shop. You need to be <strong>18+</strong>, you need <strong>500 followers</strong> to unlock shoppable videos, and <strong>1,000 followers</strong> for Live Shopping. Your account has to be in good standing (no active violations), and that's pretty much it. No inventory to buy. No products to stock. No overheads. You can start with stuff you already own and a flexible schedule — this is genuinely one of the most accessible ways to earn money online right now.</p>

