  <details style="margin:0.3em 0; padding:0.5em 0.8em; background:#fff; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #e3e8ef; cursor:pointer;"><summary>B) You unlock higher commission rates via TAP</summary><p style="margin:0.5em 0 0 0; color:#2f855a;">✓ Correct. TAP (TikTok Affiliate Partner) gives bound creators access to higher-commission campaigns.</p></details>
  <details style="margin:0.3em 0; padding:0.5em 0.8em; background:#fff; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid #e3e8ef; cursor:pointer;"><summary>C) Your videos get priority on the For You Page</summary><p style="margin:0.5em 0 0 0; color:#c53030;">✗ Binding is about commissions, not algorithm boosts.</p></details>
