<p style="line-height:1.7; color:#2d3748;">A quick recap of what you've just learned: <strong>The Vehicle</strong> — a clear understanding of the 4 ways to sell on TikTok Shop. <strong>The Fuel</strong> — the difference between Affiliate and UGC income (and why you can stack them). <strong>The Engine</strong> — what binding is and why TAP commissions are a game-changer. And <strong>The Mindset</strong> — a commitment to the long game, where input beats output every time. Next up: Lesson 2, where we get into product selection and how to avoid bans. See you there.</p>
